/* ===================================================
USE THIS TO COME UP WITH NOTES FOR GAME

** A SIMPLE GAME **
A small and simple crafting (or alchemy) game 

In general, the player will always be brought to the main screen. Here, they
can go to their inventory, or the help screen, or the shortcut screen, or the 
crafting screen, or quit the game...

crafting -- where the player will crafting their items
inventory -- see the items that the player has already collected
help -- tells the player basic commands to play the game
exit -- exits and quits the game
shortcut -- the screen where the player can scee possible shortcut codes for the
            other screens



====================================================== */
